headline: Campbell Global Acquires Emerald Ridge Timberland in Oregon's Pacific Northwest
summary: (NYSE: JPM) Campbell Global, LLC, the timberland investment manager of J.P. Morgan Asset Management, today announced the successful acquisition of Emerald Ridge, a premier timberland property spanning approximately 28,200 acres (11,400 hectares) across the north coastal and Willamette Valley regions of Oregon.

headline: Salient Wins Hall of Innovation Award at JPMorganChase Technology Innovation Symposium
summary: Salient has been inducted into JPMorganChase's Hall of Innovation at the firm's 17th annual Technology Innovation Symposium. The symposium brought together over 200 CEOs, founders and venture capital investors with JPMorganChase's leadership team to discuss strategic technology direction and key industry trends.
